caption:
What sets custom designers apart from one another??

I know there are a bunch of designers out there, shoot they popping up left and right. 

And while I know I’m not the most expensive designer… I’m also not the cheapest. 

I’ve designed some style pieces that you’ve seen all over the Instagram. 

But the ONE THING  that sets me apart from the rest is my personality!!! 

I can’t count how many times my customers come into the studio and WE HAVE A TIME! We chat, we laugh, we hug and sometimes we cry. 

My clients leave saying “you mad cool, your personality is chill”. 

And that’s my favorite part of the work I do. It’s the one on one experience where we have a GOOD OLE TIME! 

For all those who haven’t been able to experience VJ COUTURE, join me as I begin to go live so we can chat, chill and sew together! 

What days and time work best for everyone to log in?
